a-copyright" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199636/apple-anthropic-nvidia-salesforce-youtube-videos-training-data-copyright</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T11:02:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T11:02:01-04:00</updated><title>以下是您可以花费 50 美元或更少的价格获得的一些 Prime Day 科技优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K Max 侧放在靠红墙的桌子上的特写照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/S83NB80DP5nMxWf3pREYvkkdxhs=/0x1:3008x2006/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73463922/Amazon_Fire_TV_Stick_4K_Max_2023_Lifestyle_图片.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊最新的 Fire TV Stick 4K Max 可以在闲置时展示艺术品和小部件，Prime Day 仅需 34.99 美元。&lt;/em>; |图片：亚马逊&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NoWnhe&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-guide-2024&quot; >;亚马逊 Prime Day 已正式到来&lt;/a>;，带来了涵盖所有价位和类别的大量优惠。尽管科技领域的许多最大折扣都是为优质降噪耳机和电视保留的，但对于那些想要购买的人来说，仍然有大量经济实惠的小玩意和小玩意儿在打折&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.amazon.com/deal/c8962315&quot;>;便宜的基础知识&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Amazfit-Fitness-Tracker-Monitoring-Resistant/dp/B09Z6CRHJ6 ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;健身带&lt;/a>;，或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/God-War-Ragnar%C3 %B6k-PlayStation-4/dp/B0B61ZQFF5?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;一个&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. amazon.com/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-Version/dp/B0C8VKNJ1B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;的&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.amazon.com/Armored-Core-VI-Fires-Rubicon-PlayStation/dp/B0BX4KZ5PJ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;几个&lt;/a>; AAA适用于 Nintendo Switch、Xbox Series X / S 或 PlayStation 5 的游戏。&lt;/p>; 